      "acceptanceCriteria": "SQA plan documented; version control and regression testing in place for CFD solver.",
      "rationale": "The CFD solver (ANSYS Fluent 19.2) is a commercially validated code with documented SQA procedures. Version control logs and regression test suite results confirm software integrity at the revision used for this study."
    },
    {
      "factorStandard": "ASME-VV40-2018",
      "factorType": "Numerical code verification",
      "type": "CredibilityFactor",
