      "factorStatus": "assessed",
      "acceptanceCriteria": "Order-of-accuracy tests pass for relevant flow regimes; manufactured solution benchmarks documented.",
      "rationale": "Numerical code verification was performed using method of manufactured solutions for the incompressible Navier-Stokes equations. Observed order of accuracy matched theoretical second-order convergence for all primary flow variables."
    },
    {
