    "rationale": "The credibility assessment for COU1 is Accepted. Seven of thirteen credibility factors were assessed at MRL 2; all assessed factors met or exceeded their required credibility levels. The remaining six factors were either not-assessed or scoped out consistent with MRL 2 requirements. The CFD model is determined to be sufficiently credible for identifying worst-case hemolysis operating conditions for the Class II CPB device.",
